Class Message

  • java.lang.Object
    • play.db.jpa.JPABase
      • play.db.jpa.GenericModel
        • play.db.jpa.Model
          • models.Message
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, play.db.Model

    @Entity
public class Message
extends play.db.jpa.Model
    This is the model representing a message. It is a ManyToOne relationship to a Chat object. Each Message has a String msg representing the message content. Message objects are created upon hitting send
